ler","resilience","resiliency-patterns","retry-strategies","transient-fault-handling"],"visibility":"public","forks":1263,"open_issues":7,"watchers":14028,"default_branch":"main","permissions":{"admin":false,"maintain":false,"push":false,"triage":false,"pull":true}},"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly/pulls/2590","html_url":"https://github.com/App-vNext/Polly/pull/2590","diff_url":"https://github.com/App-vNext/Polly/pull/2590.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/App-vNext/Polly/pull/2590.patch","merged_at":"2025-04-15T21:38:49Z"},"body":"- Update the copyright year in `LICENSE`.\r\n- Include the `LICENSE` file within the NuGet packages.\r\n- Update `Copyright` to match the `LICENSE` file.\r\n\r\nResolves #2579.\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly/issues/2590/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly/issues/2590/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly/issues/comments/2805404171","html_url":"https://github.com/App-vNext/Polly/issues/2579#issuecomment-2805404171","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly/issues/2579","id":2805404171,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAJaD5s6nNxIL","user":{"login":"martincostello","id":1439341,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzkzNDE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1439341?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello","html_url":"https://github.com/martincostello","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2025-04-15T14:23:51Z","updated_at":"2025-04-15T14:24:35Z","body":"Would this meet your needs?\n\n`LICENSE` is in the NuGet package:\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b910d78c-cf5e-4243-970a-a237528e7df5)\n\nThe copyright matches the text from that file:\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c75e3b18-32fa-4307-a6cb-46acf93fccf9)\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/62f46405-60ec-401e-8f80-2b45e4c7501a)\n\nThe `.nuspec`\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<package xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2012/06/nuspec.xsd\">\n  <metadata>\n    <id>Polly.Core</id>\n    <version>8.5.3-pr.2590.4610</version>\n    <authors>Michael Wolfenden,App vNext</authors>\n    <owners></owners>\n    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>\n    <license type=\"file\">LICENSE</license>\n    <icon>package-icon.png</icon>\n    <readme>package-readme.md</readme>\n    <projectUrl>https://github.com/App-vNext/Polly</projectUrl>\n    <description>Polly.Core is a .NET resilience and transient-fault-handling library that allows developers to express resilience strategies such as Retry, Circuit Breaker, Hedging, Timeout, Chaos and Fallback in a fluent and thread-safe manner.</description>\n    <releaseNotes>See https://github.com/App-vNext/Polly/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md for details</releaseNotes>\n    <copyright>Copyright (c) 2015-2025, App vNext</copyright>\n    <tags>Polly Simmy Exception Handling Resilience Transient Fault Policy Circuit Breaker CircuitBreaker Chaos ChaosEngineering Retry Wait Fallback Timeout Parallelization Hedging</tags>\n    <repository type=\"git\" url=\"https://github.com/App-vNext/Polly\" commit=\"b42d8d95f362a31c6ee9579dec4e189887a09c11\" />\n    <dependencies>\n      <group targetFramework=\".NETFramework4.6.2\">\n        <dependency id=\"Microsoft.Bcl.AsyncInterfaces\" version=\"6.0.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"Microsoft.Bcl.TimeProvider\" version=\"8.0.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"System.ComponentModel.Annotations\" version=\"4.5.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"System.Threading.Tasks.Extensions\" version=\"4.5.4\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"System.ValueTuple\" version=\"4.5.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n      </group>\n      <group targetFramework=\".NETFramework4.7.2\">\n        <dependency id=\"Microsoft.Bcl.AsyncInterfaces\" version=\"6.0.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"Microsoft.Bcl.TimeProvider\" version=\"8.0.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"System.ComponentModel.Annotations\" version=\"4.5.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"System.Threading.Tasks.Extensions\" version=\"4.5.4\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"System.ValueTuple\" version=\"4.5.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n      </group>\n      <group targetFramework=\"net6.0\">\n        <dependency id=\"Microsoft.Bcl.TimeProvider\" version=\"8.0.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n      </group>\n      <group targetFramework=\"net8.0\" />\n      <group targetFramework=\".NETStandard2.0\">\n        <dependency id=\"Microsoft.Bcl.AsyncInterfaces\" version=\"6.0.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"Microsoft.Bcl.TimeProvider\" version=\"8.0.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"System.ComponentModel.Annotations\" version=\"4.5.0\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n        <dependency id=\"System.Threading.Tasks.Extensions\" version=\"4.5.4\" exclude=\"Build,Analyzers\" />\n      </group>\n    </dependencies>\n  </metadata>\n</package>\n```\n\nMy only reservation here is that it isn't immediately possible from the NuGet package to determine how Polly is licensed anymore. You can get the license, but you need to parse/read it to determine how we're licensed. Alternatively you can query the GitHub API to get it and rely on GitHub parsing it and creating an appropriate SPDX. That doesn't _need_ an API token, other than to avoid rate-limiting.\n\n```pwsh\n❯ gh api https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly --jq '.license.spdx_id'\nBSD-3-Clause\n```\n\nIt's not possible to create a NuGet package that contains the `LICENSE` file _and_ declares an explicit SPDX ([NuGet Error NU5033](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/nuget/reference/errors-and-warnings/nu5033)).\n\nI think I would prefer reverting the LICENSE change and sticking with the SPDX and we just keep the part that keeps the copyright text consistent.\n","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly/issues/comments/2805404171/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"martincostello","id":1439341,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzkzNDE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1439341?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello","html_url":"https://github.com/martincostello","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/martincostello/subscriptions","organizations_url":"